## For Lutirs to utilize Proton. 
## Link the Proton files from your steam to your Lutris client
## Linking avoids the need to constantly updated the Lutris version of Proton (Note the -s flag is to override the file in the Lutris)
ln -s $HOME/.local/share/Steam/steamapps/common/Proton*/dist $HOME/.local/share/lutris/runners/wine/proton
